  "description": "Professional ultra-high resolution 8K photogrammetry-based nature textures for AAA game development and cinematic production. This comprehensive pack includes photo-scanned bark, leaves, rocks, soil, grass, moss, and ground surfaces with complete PBR material workflows. All textures feature 16-bit color depth, multiple LOD variants, displacement maps, and are optimized for both real-time rendering and offline ray-tracing. Scanned from real-world locations using professional photogrammetry equipment with color-calibrated workflows. Includes seasonal variations and weathering states.",
